      <title>TensorFlow-Plan</title>
      <link href="/2019/02/15/TensorFlow-Plan/"/>
      <url>/2019/02/15/TensorFlow-Plan/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="TensorFlow-Example"><a href="#TensorFlow-Example" class="headerlink" title="TensorFlow-Example"></a>TensorFlow-Example</h1><p>大型攻略, 从TensorFlow-Example上手TensorFlow和DL。</p><a id="more"></a><p><a href="https://github.com/aymericdamien/TensorFlow-Examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/aymericdamien/TensorFlow-Examples/</a><br><a href="https://github.com/exacity/deeplearningbook-chinese" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/exacity/deeplearningbook-chinese</a></p><h2 id="基础篇"><a href="#基础篇" class="headerlink" title="基础篇"></a>基础篇</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox" checked> TensorFlow 基本流程结构 (<a href="../TensorFlow-Note">2019.2.15</a>)</li></ul><h2 id="工具篇"><a href="#工具篇" class="headerlink" title="工具篇"></a>工具篇</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> 保存加载模型</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> tensorboard_basic</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> tensorboard_advanced</li></ul><h2 id="模型篇"><a href="#模型篇" class="headerlink" title="模型篇"></a>模型篇</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> linear_regression 线性回归 (<a href="../TensorFlow-Examples-LR">working</a>)</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> logistic_regression 逻辑回归</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> nearest_neighbor 最近邻</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox" checked> kmeans K均值聚类</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> random_forest 随机森林</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> gradient_boosted_decision_tree 梯度提升决策树</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> word2vec 词向量</li></ul><h2 id="神经网络"><a href="#神经网络" class="headerlink" title="神经网络"></a>神经网络</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> autoencoder 自编码器</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> variational_autoencoder 变分自编码器</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> convolutional_network 卷积神经网路</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> convolutional_network_raw ？</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> gan 生成式对抗网络</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> dcgan 深度卷积生成对抗网络</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> dynamic_rnn 动态递归神经网络</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> recurrent_network 递回神经网路</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> bidirectional_rnn 双向递回神经网路</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> multilayer_perceptron 多层感知机</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> neural_network 神经网络</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> neural_network_raw ？</li></ul><h2 id="有生之年"><a href="#有生之年" class="headerlink" title="有生之年"></a>有生之年</h2><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> eager</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> dataset</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> GPU</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
